Eitobira Haman pee eidaikie Ilyahudi


1  Ore te siadi kuna baa, neilepie olaiguanani Serser Haman le Agag, olayioni le Hamedata, neisho ninye enkitoo nepik olorika lenye shumata ile lelo kituaak ooboitare ninye. 
2  Ore laisiaayiak pooki lo laiguanani ootii kishomi neirrugo aaisho Haman enkanyit; amu neijia apa eitanapishe olaiguanani ajo. Kake eitu eirrugo Mordekai arashu aitodolu enkanyit. 
3  Nejoki lelo aisiaayiak lo laiguanani ootii kishomi Mordekai, “Kainyoo pee igil enkitanapata o laiguanani?” 
4  Ore pee eirorie ninche ninye anaake neany ening ninche, neliki ninche Haman, ejo pee edol tenaa kepal Mordekai nena, amu etiaaka ninye ninche nchere Olyahudi ninye. 
5  Ore pee edol Haman ajo eitu eirrugo Mordekai arashu eitodolu enkanyit negoro oleng. 
6  Kake eitu ejo aar Mordekai aa ninye ake. Amu eitayioloki ninye iltung'ana pooki le Mordekai, neing'oru Haman pee ear Ilyahudi pooki, iltung'ana le Mordekai, te nkitoria pooki e Serser.


7  Ore to lapa le dukuya, laa ninye olapa le Nisan, to lari le tomon oare lo laiguanani Serser, neosh ninche Pura nchere enkukuo te dukuya Haman nkolong'i pooki; neosh too lapaitin pooki o metabaiki olapa le tomon oare, laa ninye olapa le Adar. 
8  Neitoki Haman ajoki olaiguanani Serser, “Etii iltung'ana moobo ooisardakari aaorikino atua iltung'ana loo loshon pooki le nkitoria ino; ore nkitanapat enye nepaashare inoo lkulikae tung'ana pooki, nemeibung nkitanapat o laiguanani, metaa metumie olaiguanani dupoto te nepalaa ninche. 
9  Te neishiaakino to laiguanani nchoo meigeri enkitanapata pee emuti ninche, naa kalak nanu ntalantani nkalifuni tomon oo mpisai apik nkaik e lelo ooitasheiki esiaai o laiguanani pee eyau aapik atua masaa o laiguanani.” 
10  Neitayu olaiguanani olgisoi ashurtu te nkaina enye neisho Haman le Agag ole Hamedata, olmang'atinta loo Lyahudi. 
11  Nejoki olaiguanani Haman, “Kinchooki mpisai, o ltung'ana sii, pee intaas ninche anaa enaishiaakino te iyie.”


12  Neipoti ilaigerok lo laiguanani te nkolong e tomon ookuni o lapa le dukuya, neigeri anaa enaitanapishe Haman neigerokini lelo ang'eni o lelo kituaak ooitasheiki iloshon, o laitasheikinok pooki loo ltung'ana, olosho ake to rorei lenye o ltung'ana te nkutuk enye; neigeroki apa te nkarna e Serser nepiki olmishire te ilo gisoi lo laiguanani. 
13  Neirriwari mpala too nkaik e lelo ooirriwari meshomo ilkerenketi pooki lo laiguanani, pee eidaikie, neari metuata, neiwuang'ieki Ilyahudi pooki ooti o lbotoro, inkituaak o nkera, te nkolong nabo, te nkolong e tomon ookuni o lapa le tomon oare, laa ninye olapa le Adar, neya imasaa enye. 
14  Naa keirriwari empalai e ilo kigeroto iloshon pooki pee eitanapi metolikini iltung'ana pooki meterretenata te ina olong. 
15  Nepuo lelo ooirriwari aaya mpala te nkisarrisar te nkitanapata o laiguanani, neitayuni ina kitanapata te Susa teina ang kitok. Netoni olaiguanani o Haman aaokisho, kake ore ina ang anasa e Susa neaku enking'asia.

